start rxvtd in a race-free way
Try "rxvtd -f -o", which tells rxvtd to open the display, create the listening socket and then fork.

= cURL =
： curl -O http://blog.terac.com/andy/index.html
： curl -c -O http://blog.terac.com/andy/index.html
： curl -O http://www.sitename.com/photo[001-100].JPG

